00:52:11.140 --> 00:52:14.470 align:middle line:84%
Because it's, like, one
village, or one person.

00:52:14.470 --> 00:52:17.260 align:middle line:84%
And they're pretty
much in isolation.

00:52:17.260 --> 00:52:20.800 align:middle line:84%
Here, it's still
