give you money, and likewise,

00:54:12.140 --> 00:54:14.430 align:middle line:90%
vice versa.

00:54:14.430 --> 00:54:17.120 align:middle line:90%
And that's not self-insurance.

00:54:17.120 --> 00:54:21.710 align:middle line:84%
That's kind of dynamics
of explicit risk-sharing

00:54:21.710 --> 00:54:22.580 align:middle line:90%
insurance.

